OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,FLuke Simon tells ITV News' Richard
OL,7,FPayne how he and his brother Piers
OL,8,Fwere 'inseparable'
OL,10,FA man who lost his brother in the 2004
OL,11,FBoxing Day tsunami has returned to the
OL,12,Fscene of the disaster 20 years after
OL,13,Fthe wave struck.
OL,15,FLuke Simon, from Somerset, who was 30
OL,16,Fat the time, was celebrating Christmas
OL,17,Fwith his brother Piers and three
OL,18,Ffriends on the island of Ko Phi Phi,
OL,19,Fin Thailand, when the tsunami hit.
