OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,F"The wave came straight for us," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "If we looked ahead, where we
OL,8,Fshould have seen market and buildings
OL,9,Fand palm trees, suddenly the whole
OL,10,Fhorizon was boiling and bubbling up in
OL,11,Ffront of us".
OL,13,FLuke said he spent five days searching
OL,14,Ffor his brother in the aftermath of
OL,15,Fthe disaster, until his body was
OL,16,Feventually found on New Year's Eve.
OL,18,FHe then faced the heartbreaking task
OL,19,Fof calling his parents in Somerset to
OL,20,Fbreak the news.
