OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,FLuke has been recalling what happened
OL,7,Fon the day of the tsunami as part of
OL,8,Fan ITV documentary which will be aired
OL,9,Fnext week, commemorating the 20th
OL,10,Fanniversary of the disaster.
OL,12,FThe tsunami was triggered by an
OL,13,Fearthquake off the coast of Indonesia
OL,14,Fwhich registered a magnitude of up to
OL,15,F9.3.
OL,17,FNearly a quarter of a million people
OL,18,Fwere killed and around two million
OL,19,Fpeople were left homeless across 14
OL,20,Fcountries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
