OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,F"This year I've been more emotional
OL,7,Fthan any other year I would say,
OL,8,Fbecause we've been involved in things
OL,9,Fthat really are marking the 20th
OL,10,Fanniversary," Luke said.
OL,12,FTwo decades after the wave struck,
OL,13,FLuke has returned to the island of Ko
OL,14,FPhi Phi as part of the documentary.
OL,16,F"The spirit of the island is still
OL,17,Fthere, I would say, so when I was on
OL,18,FPhi Phi, I didn't feel like I was
OL,19,Fbeing transported back to the tsunami".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
