OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,F"I felt like I was being transported
OL,7,Fback to the really fun island where we
OL,8,Fwere having a great time".
OL,10,FUpon arriving back in the UK after the
OL,11,Ftsunami, Luke set up a charity in
OL,12,FPiers' memory, which initially aimed
OL,13,Fto support the people of Thailand, but
OL,14,Fnow sends school supplies to
OL,15,Fdisadvantaged children around the
OL,16,Fworld.
