OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,F20 years on, Luke still runs the
OL,7,Fcharity School in a Bag and has
OL,8,Fdelivered more than 150,000 school
OL,9,Fbags containing stationery, learning
OL,10,Fresources, eating utensils, and
OL,11,Fhygiene kits to children across 57
OL,12,Fcountries.
OL,14,FHe said the charity has now received
OL,15,Fadditional funding, which he hopes
OL,16,Fwill enable them to include more items
OL,17,Fin the school bags such as sports kits
OL,18,Fand digital technology.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
