OL,3,CSomerset man returns to Thailand 20
OL,4,Cyears after Boxing Day tsunami
OL,6,F"I feel like we've built a foundation
OL,7,Fin 20 years, and now we're at a point
OL,8,Fwhere we've got some funding, and
OL,9,Fwe've got personnel involved where we
OL,10,Fcan really start making it bigger and
OL,11,Fthat's exciting," Luke said.
OL,13,FHe added: "Knowing what we're doing in
OL,14,FPiers' memory, and that in 30 years
OL,15,Fwe'll still be doing it, you know
OL,16,Fthat's a nice feeling, as we keep
OL,17,Fremembering him".
OL,19,FTsunami: The Wave That Shook the World
OL,20,Fairs on 27 December on ITV1 and ITVX.
